              they deserve from contributors! You
              can start creating your collection below.
            </p>

            <p> <strong class="medium">We are looking forward to seeing your collection on <a
                  href="https://contribute.to" class="medium">Contribute.to</a>!
              </strong><br>Your <a href="https://contribute.to" class="gray-link">Contribute.to</a> team</p>
            {{> button type='primary' align='center' url='{{linkToUserAccount}}' title='Create Your Collection Now' }}
